{"tid":323890,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"識唔識人好驚貓","createTime":"2017-07-16T04:16:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T14:43:44.000Z","uid":126232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"02961cec7ce1dcaedf6fee372056cce7793e6a61","tid":323890,"uid":126232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"原來真係有人好驚貓（情況同亂馬差唔多），<br />\n有兩個外表好豪邁、自稱咩都唔驚既朋友原本好驚貓，<br />\n仲要驚得好誇張，見到中文字「貓」都會驚，街邊見到流浪貓無端端行過，佢會驚到成個人彈起，之後仲要驚好耐，好似撞鬼咁，<br />\n大家識唔識呢種人？"},{"pid":"d8042a598fb7b77bc1167f993635afb98476c978","tid":323890,"uid":67272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"有個friend乜柒都驚，所有動物都驚<br />\n都唔知驚乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以佢性格係真驚非扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗類似恐懼症個類<br />\n我自己都有奇奇怪怪既野驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  驚車速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一感受到尢其企起身開得太快就會標冷汗驚撞車<br />\n仲有個friend驚蝴蝶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話以前俾成堆蝴蝶圍過<br />\n係佢身行走，好驚個觸感，之此佢都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲怕貓抓，所以驚貓<br />\n其實無乜所謂每個人經歷唔同，有野怕好正常<br />\n不過知佢點解怕之後覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d0a059194a56ab067942593d955549d0f0ddc44","tid":323890,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:00:18.000Z","msg":"我驚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2726df5d8a793ad38466c7056d4e79838d94dd","tid":323890,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T11:28:58.000Z","msg":"我堂妹係咁，好驚細隻過佢的動物<br />\n試過隻貓係佢隔離行過都即刻驚到喊"},{"pid":"dbcb2a6d03d58411e6e9a1552e26e6be96d70ce5","tid":323890,"uid":65128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"713e00a835cf522fe59b6acc60a28bf30c680796","tid":323890,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"識人覺得貓眼咁大好恐怖<br />\n見到大頭相都驚"},{"pid":"4473d8b2c5596e3668ec587daf84fcdd37c4d58b","tid":323890,"uid":16161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"我都好驚蝴蝶，見到相都會打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8833d7bdc8f5f67da07c3a7af78da889ce1338f","tid":323890,"uid":57568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T16:47:31.000Z","msg":"有朋友好驚雀仔"},{"pid":"cb70a5664a6eb925377c99481a9f5c26cf7f8155","tid":323890,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:08:15.000Z","msg":"有人自稱好驚貓<br />\n唔比屋企人養貓<br />\n後來搬出去同人住自己走去養貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a8d0c538253156ecba582a7f6712497899be7d","tid":323890,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:26:14.000Z","msg":"驚蝴蝶同仙人掌<br />\n但偏偏去左兩個月周街仙人掌既地方"},{"pid":"84c95e1f40e195666b9f9360a0fc3484b422ddbe","tid":323890,"uid":116050,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"我阿妹係，佢一見到貓就瘋狂大叫，佢係真係好驚果種，佢天不怕地不怕，就係驚貓(=￣&omega;￣=)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7bf994e94a6c37369656ee59a8bc82f61dc4f5e","tid":323890,"uid":839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:35:15.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 斬柴仔 )"},{"pid":"28a22403ae78c66d30fc3515ad8efda160f71146","tid":323890,"uid":58935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好驚蝴蝶，見到相都會打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大對翼嘅都驚 例如飛蛾"},{"pid":"4caeaae9b56e661fd1dc8eca5198c7c891295f7c","tid":323890,"uid":61005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>( Show Blocked User - 斬柴仔 )</blockquote><br />\n( Show Blocked User - 斬柴仔 )"},{"pid":"de063ff1770f458273027c9a107de64847a43826","tid":323890,"uid":126232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識人覺得貓眼咁大好恐怖<br />\n見到大頭相都驚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我果兩個朋友都係勁驚貓眼"},{"pid":"08acf5eadea6e01ac29b615ffafd5cc9e2fdd63a","tid":323890,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>( Show Blocked User - 斬柴仔 )</blockquote><br />\n( Show Blocked User - 斬柴仔 )</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a06c7d46034ec1caf8d06378016bcf956b843468","tid":323890,"uid":102151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"我識有貓驚人<br />\n其實係驚我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9daf9ae7e7abac0de7d31e2b942385c0c00810","tid":323890,"uid":60648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T14:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我堂妹係咁，好驚細隻過佢的動物<br />\n試過隻貓係佢隔離行過都即刻驚到喊</blockquote><br />\n即係獅子 老虎 大象 係佢身邊行過就唔怕？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}